# ── Production reference (Cloudflare Worker + GitHub Actions) ──
# Do NOT commit real values. Do NOT enable DEV_PREVIEW here.
#
# Placement:
#   GitHub Secrets     → TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, QBITTORRENT_USERNAME,
#                        QBITTORRENT_PASSWORD, CRON_SECRET,
#                        CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN, CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID
#   GitHub Variables   → ALLOWED_TELEGRAM_USER_IDS, QBITTORRENT_URL, APP_URL
#   Worker Secrets     → synced by Deploy (all except APP_URL / CLOUDFLARE_*)
#
# See docs/DEPLOY.md and README env table.

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
ALLOWED_TELEGRAM_USER_IDS=
QBITTORRENT_URL=https://your-qb.example.com
QBITTORRENT_USERNAME=
QBITTORRENT_PASSWORD=
CRON_SECRET=

# Optional Worker secret — iOS home-screen / Safari Web App bearer auth.
# WEB_APP_TOKEN=

# GitHub Actions Variable only (webhook / Menu Button). Not a Worker secret.
APP_URL=https://tg-dl.your-subdomain.workers.dev

# GitHub Secrets only (Actions deploy), not Worker runtime:
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
